snippet.title: Shri Narendra Modi Oath Ceremony Live | Modi's Cabinet 2024 Oath Live | Modi 3.0
snippet.description:
Shri Narendra Modi took oath as the Prime Minister of India for third consecutive time. The cabinet ministers also took oath at the swearing-in ceremony at the Rashtrapati Bhawan. President Smt Droupadi Murmu administered the oath to the Prime Minister and his ministerial colleagues.

snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | SEMI-FINALS 1 | Day 4 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to SEMI-FINALS 1 of the BGIS 2024! 

Prepare to be thrilled as 16 fierce teams from ROUND 04 and 16 contenders from WILDCARD ENTRY clash in the ultimate esports showdown! üî•

BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024. It's a battlefield where legends #makewaves. With a whopping prize pool of INR 2 Crores, stakes are higher than ever.

Stay tuned! Witness emerging stars rise to fame and write their names in the BGIS history. Who will dominate? Who will surprise? Join us at 3:30 PM from Thursday to Sunday.


Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to keep up with all the action. Your favourite players need your cheers, so drop your support in the comments below!


#MAKEWAVES  #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA  #INDIAKAGAME

snippet.description:
Welcome to SEMI-FINALS 1 of the BGIS 2024! 

Prepare to be thrilled as 16 fierce teams from ROUND 04 and 16 contenders from WILDCARD ENTRY clash in the ultimate esports showdown! üî•

BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024. It's a battlefield where legends #makewaves. With a whopping prize pool of INR 2 Crores, stakes are higher than ever.

Stay tuned! Witness emerging stars rise to fame and write their names in the BGIS history. Who will dominate? Who will surprise? Join us at 3:30 PM from Thursday to Sunday.


Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell to keep up with all the action. Your favourite players need your cheers, so drop your support in the comments below!

snippet.description:
India (IND) vs Pakistan (PAK), T20 World Cup 2024: India have been bundled out for 119 in 20 overs, their lowest total in a T20 World Cup match. Rishabh Pant top-scored for the 2007 champions, but the rest of the batters failed. Naseem Shah and Mohammad Amir delivered with the ball, picking up 6 wickets between them.

snippet.title: Empowering Girls | Beti Bachao Beti Padhao | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
Beti Bachao Beti Padhao" (BBBP) is a campaign launched by the Government of India aimed at addressing the issues of gender discrimination and promoting the education of girls. The name translates to "Save the Daughter, Educate the Daughter." The campaign was initiated in January 2015 and is a joint effort of the Ministry of Women and Child Development, the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare, and the Ministry of Education.

Produced by
District Administration, Chumoukedima, Nagaland

Thanks to Christina Memorial Higher Secondary School for allowing us to shoot in your school.

________________________________________

Cricket is a bat-and-ball game played between two teams of eleven players. A 22-yard (20-meter) pitch has a wicket at each end, two bails balanced on three stumps. The batting side scores runs by striking the ball bowled at the wicket with the bat (and running between the wickets). In contrast, the bowling and fielding side tries to prevent this (by preventing the ball from leaving the field and getting the ball to either wicket) and dismiss each batter (so they are "out"). Means of dismissal include bowling when the ball hits the stumps and dislodges the bails. The innings ended when ten batters were dismissed, and the teams swapped roles. The game is adjudicated by two umpires, aided by a third umpire and match referee in international matches.

Forms of cricket range from Twenty20, with each team batting for a single inning of 20 overs, to Test matches played over five days. Traditionally, cricketers play in an all-white kit but wear club or team colors in limited-overs cricket. In addition to the basic kit, some players wear protective gear to prevent injury caused by the ball. A complex, solid spheroid made of compressed leather with a slightly raised sewn seam enclosing a cork core layered tightly wound string.
________________________________________

snippet.title: ‡§ò‡§∞ ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§Ü‡§Æ ‡§ï‡•à‡§∏‡•á ‡§™‡§ï‡§æ‡§è - Home Made Mangoes - Ripen at home
snippet.description:
"Easy Steps to Ripen Mangoes at Home | Enjoy Sweet and Juicy Mangoes Anytime!"

Welcome to our channel! Are you craving sweet, juicy mangoes but found yourself with unripe ones? Don't worry, we've got you covered! In this video, we'll guide you through simple and effective methods to ripen mangoes at home, so you can indulge in their deliciousness whenever you want.

Mangoes are a tropical delight loved by many, but waiting for them to ripen can sometimes be a test of patience. Fortunately, with our tips and tricks, you can accelerate the ripening process and enjoy ripe, succulent mangoes in no time.

In this tutorial, we'll share various methods including:

1. Paper Bag Method: Learn how enclosing mangoes in a paper bag with a ripe banana or apple can speed up the ripening process by trapping ethylene gas.
2. Rice Method: Discover how placing mangoes in a container filled with rice can help them ripen faster due to the heat generated by the rice.
3. Warm Water Method: Find out how soaking mangoes in warm water can soften them and enhance their sweetness.

Follow along with us step by step as we demonstrate each method, providing helpful tips and insights along the way. Whether you're preparing mango salsa, smoothies, or simply enjoying them fresh, ripe mangoes will elevate your culinary experience.

Say goodbye to waiting days for your mangoes to ripen on the counter. With our easy techniques, you'll have perfectly ripe mangoes ready to enjoy in as little as 24-48 hours.

Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe for more helpful tips and delicious recipes. Let's ripen those mangoes and dive into tropical paradise together!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4105 - Abdul Ne Liya Gokuldham Chodkar Jane Ka Faisla?! I Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta.
